Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:07.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watching Fairy Tail keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:13.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:17.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reitei Lyon is Gray's former fellow pupil and is plotting to resurrect Deliora! {I couldn't think of a way to add the "older" meaning without wedging it in}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:23.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was their master, Ul, who sealed it using a spell that turns your own body into ice, Iced Shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:25.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who killed Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:29.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon... Do we live together or die together? {note, the Japanese is also flipped from the line in the previous episode.... sheesh}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for even more who-knows-what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:41.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to mystery is right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:44.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world's a wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,which we're already wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:52.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement gets my heart racing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:59.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What is real, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see tomorrow, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:10.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The only part leveling up is my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:15.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just throw away our daily life together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:23.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! S. O. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:29.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Living itself will be our training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:32.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for even more who-knows-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:40.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be satisfied with just the normal answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical wonder life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:51.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best living our life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:10.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the guts to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:22.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Erza, everyone at Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm making my exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You break into my fight spouting "responsibility?" Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be takin' my kill! {I don't pick up that it isn't literal, but Natsu often goes overboard in his dialog, so it isn't a problem. I like the translation.}{kill might be a bit harsh here, but in the pseudo RPG world here I think it's understood that it's not a literal "kill"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:48.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that's gonna beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:51.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you that I'd take him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:54.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And did I ever say, "Yes, Roger that, Sir?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:03:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be the one that finishes him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:04.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:08.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when is dying finishing a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that just running away, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Galuna Island, the Final Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:38.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not allow anyone to get in the way of Reitei-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:53.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruins have un-tilted themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:04.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the light of the moon will land on Deliora again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zalty, is this your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:15.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon will be out soon, so I returned the temple to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is he? {I know that Zalty's real identity is a female, but I'm pretty sure all the characters assume it's a he at this point.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:20.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all my hard work tilting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you fix it back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you fix it back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:33.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we should begin the Moon Drip ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignored?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:39.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's {\i1}on{\i0}, masked-man! {It's cool with me.}{a bit of a white-washing of "namahage", but it fits with the line...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, bub!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:47.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wallop that bastard a million times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You handle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost last time, and it's a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:55.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For all of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what noisome fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:15.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you count on Natsu stopping me from using Iced Shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I wouldn't imagine that guy getting anywhere near that kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:23.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just planned on taking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:26.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. But I would have been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I realized that, I said "Do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:38.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I were to be trapped in the ice, I have allies with the same goals as myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the island where you can use the Moon Drip to undo Iced Shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:48.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell is powerless here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:52.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you still wish to defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot win against-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What foolishness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First you threaten, and {\i1}then{\i0} you persuade?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:09.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your guild have some dentist that de-fangs you all? {fangs = "courage" here}{say what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell was a spell that turned her body into ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:27.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ice that sealed Deliora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:31.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The very same ice that you're trying to melt now... is Ul herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:37.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul became that ice and lives on today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:44.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not telling you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Ul that I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:55.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he knew that I became the ice, he'd probably spend his entire life trying to undo the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:04.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Lyon, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:18.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that ice is no longer Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some frozen remains!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew? {This line was my proof (when translating the manga) that Lyon doesn't think it's a lie.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You honestly believe that Ul is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:38.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! How can you move with such a wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of trying to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll attempt to defeat me, the elder pupil?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:12.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been holding back for my battle with Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to waste my magic power, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll settle it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, no magic, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:30.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for your opponent's weak points when fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul taught us that, remember? {match up with callback to this line by Gray at end of battle}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare speak that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:42.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, you masked-bastard! {Oh... seems my white washing before predicted the writers pretty well...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you fix the ruins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that'd work on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:05.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, that is how I returned the ruins back how they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:10.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Lost Magics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic so powerful and with such grave side-effects that they have been erased from history itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From history?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Dragon Slayer magic is also so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:22.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:28.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he go? Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You were gonna finish it with your fists, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah... There was a guy I fought like this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:53.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:55.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:07.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that should stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end! {Chibi Erza is so cute!... sorry...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:43.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you were no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have died a long time ago! {Naw, your line is good.} {This is a bit tricky... it's literally "you 'person who failed to die when he should have'"... I think it's referring both to when he challenged Deliora and just before when he was going to use Iced Shell... But it's a serious insult in Japanese (probably derived from disgraced samurais that failed going through with suicide or something)... Maybe just something like "Go to hell!" is better (that's one of the definitions in the green goddess, anyway)}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:59.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not while I haven't shown him I'm the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:24.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand... losing to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose! I'll defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that sky was so blue it got on my nerves... {mukatsuku hodo means "so *blank* it makes me angry"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, have you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:16.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be a lot of them, but their magical power is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They only have 5 real wizards among them. {I presume she's talking about Lyon, Toby, Sherry, Yuka, and Zalty?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:23.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just great... I can't get serious with these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should {\i1}you{\i0} be saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Giant Crab, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:56.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, my lady, for what might I have this pleasure-snip? {How about: "what do you command-snip?" "for what might I have this pleasure" is a little convoluted to get the point across quickly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"My lady?" say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's with the -snip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who summoned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a triple-take! {non-literal}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:07.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, make them all powerless to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay-ebi... -snip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:28.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me being brought to my knees by someone like Gray? I couldn't bear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Snow Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke our promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora'll be resurrected soon anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be able to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to stop you! {a bit too many "no matter what"s}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when Zalty has started the Moon Drip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can't even hold a candle to that jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start by burning you to a crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some fine fighting words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a good nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:45.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smell like women's perfume for some reason... {Yeah, Natsu doesn't get why. This is just a rare (for Mashima) piece of foreshadowing.}{This line might imply that Natsu realizes Zalty is a woman, but I don't really think so... Natsu's used to enough weirdoes in Fairy tail to probably not think twice about a man wearing women's perfume... Plus, using "she" would definitely spoil what is supposed to be a shocking revelation later on...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:52.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I must ensure Deliora is resurrected no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:55.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up already! It's not going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:04.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray will blow that guy away, and I'll blow you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One million times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that'll be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see... {a few too many "that"s}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is above doing the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:28.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a single person the moon drip effect is quite weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:33.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've already gathered plenty of moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:37.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a tiny bit more, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:37.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ice is melting off Deliora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something about the guy on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after me was a mistake, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My little "Salamander..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work. Let us hurry along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:05.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:12.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let you interfere with Reitei-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those hair ornaments...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:17.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the citizens of Brago, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a score to settle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:40.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use fire magic here, it will accelerate the ice melting off Deliora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:45.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could use fire magic to melt the ice, then you wouldn't have had to go through all this trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:50.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fastest to beat you here, then smash the guy up on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:58.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am surprised at how quickly you can think on your feet in the midst of a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:07.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruins are shaking again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:13.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Moon Drip ceremony has begun. The ice has started melting off Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Ul's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were not able to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:24.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how long I've waited for this moment? {actually, yes, he does}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent ten years gathering allies, knowledge, then I finally learned of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The island where you can gather the light of the moon, Galuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:42.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We transported Deliora from Brago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:48.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been doing this pointless crap for three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:51.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pointless?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rich, coming from someone who's been playing around in some guild for ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just trusted what Ul told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:09.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a ton of wizards stronger than me in the countries to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:13.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I finally arrived at Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:17.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was true. There were a ton of amazing wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. Iced Shell is a magic that is done by one's own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:31.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No magic done by a third-party has the power to melt the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:35.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are a ton of amazing wizards here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:40.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there may be one way, though... {the double negative tends to be confusing in subtitles.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. Melting the ice would be no different than killing Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think back on it, I realize that gramps was going to mention the Moon Drip, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:04.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And to think that it would be her own pupil that is trying to kill Ul! You've disappointed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived my entire life for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:17.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can a pupil surpass his teacher when she's already dead! Think about it! {the timing of his delivery indicates that the "think about it" should be last}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:23.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Deliora! If I can destroy the one thing that defeated our teacher, then I can surpass her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ambition of yours is nice, but you haven't realized you've taken a wrong turn along the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:35.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think someone as blind as you could beat Ul?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Think again! Not in 100 years! {I translated "denoushite koi" a little differently, and in my version, having it second makes sense. With your translation, having it first makes sense.}{this has more impact flipped in English, IMO}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snow Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you are, Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:56.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:20:00.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A caged beast who knows nothing of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy that Creation Magic of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Creations made with one hand are out of balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So when it counts they don't have the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Cannon! {Lyon has a line that isn't subtitled, "G-Gray..." after this line.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:37.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul taught us that, remember? {match with Lyon's line, above}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:48.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've braced it before... {I think that's what they're trying to get at. "te-oku" is to do something in advance}{they changed this line from the manga from "shiketsu" (blood clotting) to "katameru" (hardening? ) to match the censoring of blood out of the animation... But it makes the translation really weird... the original would have been something like "the blood had clotted before" but now when blood isn't involved using "clott" doesn't work... Thoughts?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:02.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My ears are ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:06.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:38.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:45.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:49.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... Has it been resurrected?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:53.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no choice then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell! {Yeah, but Natsu and Erza are around -- and Moon Drip takes a long time to do.}{wait... are you dense? Didn't you learn anything? if you use iced shell on the island they'll just undo it again... Oh shounen logic}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:02.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:05.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:15.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing after your profile left only in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:27.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "I never want to see your face again," when you left me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:32.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tears on your cheek said it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you felt like you'd be swallowed up in the waves of contradiction
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:45.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you always held back your tears, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:56.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a strong person," they said, but everyone overestimated you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:23:05.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and before you knew it you lost sight of who you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:09.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the sun I thought would always be near me collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the light shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:16.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbing out the truths and the lies of one day, altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:29.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,still, ironically, chasing after your profile in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:33.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Happy's Fairy Tail Lecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we'll be telling you the secrets of Erza, the Armored Wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:43.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Called "Titania," Erza fights by requiping different weapons and magic armor one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:47.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She has some swimsuits and other weird clothes, but she's really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:50.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still she has times when she doesn't listen to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:52.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:54.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand, Bow, Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:24:00.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you ate the fish I was planning on having, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:03.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad... I'll give you the next one I catch, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:06.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother! Our friendship is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:11.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. It's too bad, I was hoping to take you fishing with me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We could also make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, didn't you just say our friendship was over?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.56,0:24:22.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat's short term memory is very poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:24.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's sure convenient for you...
